// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1522 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bd4c22e5-017f-50ed-9e7e-b2800e97cc4e

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.04* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.10* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:13.04*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
